               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgPlanckHistory\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPlanckHistory', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: History of the universe according to the |Lambda-CDM model (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a1a7c478-9061-4160-ba43-301c081733e9",
